@startuml Upload Documentation and Confirm Sequence Diagram

actor "FE (User App)" as FE
participant "BFF (Our System)" as BFF
database "Local DB\n(partitionKey, idLavorazione, state)" as DB
box "INPS Services (PDND)" #LightBlue
  participant "MS INPS\n(GestioneDomandaCED)" as INPS
end box

title 4. Confirmation Submission (ConfermaDomanda) - UPLOADING_DOCUMENTS state

FE -> BFF: Submit Final Confirmation (idLavorazione, Dati Ulteriore Documentazione OPTIONAL)

BFF -> DB: Retrieve Record R (idLavorazione, IK_CURRENT)
DB --> BFF: R

== Local DB Write 1: Intermediate state ==
BFF -> DB: UPDATE Record R (state: UPLOADING_DOCUMENTS)

alt DB Write 1 SUCCESS
    DB --> BFF: OK

    BFF -> INPS: ConfermaDomanda(idLavorazione, Dati aggiuntivi) \n <<Header: Idempotency Key = R.IK_CURRENT>>

    alt INPS Success (HTTP 200 OK)
        INPS --> BFF: idLavorazione (X)

        == Local DB Write 2: Update to ACQUIRED ==
        BFF -> DB: UPDATE Record R (state: ACQUIRED)

        alt DB Update SUCCESS
            DB --> BFF: OK
            BFF --> FE: Success (Application acquired)

        else DB Update FAILURE (***INCONSISTENCY POINT***)
            DB --> BFF: ERROR (Timeout)
            note right of BFF: INPS has acquired application (esitoCheck=40). \nLocal DB shows UPLOADING_DOCUMENTS. \nReconciliation (Flow 1) will fix this disparity.
            BFF --> FE: System Error (HTTP 500)
        end

    else INPS Failure (HTTP 400 BAD REQUEST)
        INPS --> BFF: Error Code (e.g., 403: File Allegato superiore a 2 Mb, 115: Stato non coerente)
        BFF --> FE: Validation Error: (Details: Error Code and Description)
    end

else DB Write 1 FAILURE (Fatal Error)
    DB --> BFF: ERROR (e.g., Connection issue)
    BFF --> FE: HTTP 503 Service Unavailable
end
@enduml
